column5: i was just wondering if anybody has been up to jordan harbour recently, or if anybody is fishing?, catching? thinking of going up this weekend, dont really wanna make the trip if there isnt enough ice yet..  thanks, eric
Wide open as of yesterday...  Cheers  Craig
Are you asking about the harbour or the marina? The 2 are very different.
well i drove over the jordon harbour yesterday on my way back from Great Wolf lodge with the family and does not look like it would be safe to ice fish.
there is a thin layer of ice over most of the marina. no where close to safe.
